cURL Cheatsheet

**cURL cheatsheet** tuned to your Flask app
(CSRF on, login form, RBAC, redirects).

---

# Quick flags you’ll actually use

```bash
# Core flags
-sS            # silent but show errors
-I             # HEAD only (headers + status)
-L             # follow redirects
-D -           # dump response headers to stdout
-o /dev/null   # discard body
-w '%{http_code}\n'  # print status code
-b cookies.txt # send cookies from jar
-c cookies.txt # save cookies to jar
```

---

# Env setup

```bash
# Base URL + cookie jars per role
BASE=${BASE:-http://127.0.0.1:5000}
USER_JAR=${USER_JAR:-/tmp/vcdb_user.cookies}
ADMIN_JAR=${ADMIN_JAR:-/tmp/vcdb_admin.cookies}

# Utility: pretty status line
curlh() { curl -sS -D - -o /dev/null "$@"; }
curli() { curl -sS -I "$@"; }   # HEAD only
```

