# 1) Health checks & redirects

```bash
# healthz (expect 200)
curli "$BASE/healthz"

# root (expect 200)
curli "$BASE/"

# unauthenticated protected route (expect 302 to /auth/login?next=...)
curlh "$BASE/transactions/hello"
```

