# 4) Hitting protected routes

```bash
# after login_user
curlh -b "$USER_JAR" "$BASE/customers/hello"      # expect 200
curlh -b "$USER_JAR" "$BASE/governance/hello"     # expect 403 for non-admin

# after login_admin
curlh -b "$ADMIN_JAR" "$BASE/governance/hello"    # expect 200
```

