# 6) Transactions ledger helpers

```bash
# Verify hash chain (200 OK + {"ok":true})
curl -sS -b "$USER_JAR" "$BASE/transactions/verify" | jq .

# Filtered verify (type/slice)
curl -sS -b "$USER_JAR" "$BASE/transactions/verify?type=auth.user_role.assigned" | jq .

# Export JSONL (save to file)
curl -sS -b "$USER_JAR" -o ledger.jsonl "$BASE/transactions/export.jsonl?slice=auth"
wc -l ledger.jsonl
head -3 ledger.jsonl
```

